text: Michel Porasso (20 August 1891 - 6 August 1944) was a Monegasque gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1881 births Category:1944 deaths Category:Monegasque male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Monaco Category:Gymnasts at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
